 Armour</span><hr size=1> Hi all:<br>
<br>
I am excited about the upcomming Kael raids on Wednesday nights. I am hoping that eventually we can get you all oufitted in a nice new suit of Thurgadin armour. I just ran some numbers to see how my stats would improve with the Thurgadin Shaman armour (Rune Crafter's Armour). Needless to say, I was quite impressed.<br>
<br>
I have a pretty nice setup for a shaman now. With the rig that I wear while grouping I have roughly 800AC and 185 Wisdom unbuffed.<br>
<br>
Getting the full set of Rune Crafter's Armour will give me 44 more raw AC, 21 more wis, and 230 more mana. Wow! That is a nice increase. My defense skill is maxed, so my real AC increase will be closer to 66. The extra wisdom will put me over 200, so I can finally be free of those velium jasper rings. In their place I can wear resist jewlery or my 6ac 65hp rings, or I can quest the coldain rings and wear those. The extra mana is gravy.<br>
<br>
This armour is well within our grasp. All we have to do is show up at Kael and put in some time. I'm hoping to see lots of you show up on Wednesdays. I am also hoping that all of us being together in Velious on Wednesday night will lead to raids on other nights of the week. Let's start hitting Kael often. Those giants won't know what hit them.<br>
<br>
-Sarai <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#1478A2><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub88.ezboard.com/uskyeangel.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Skyeangel</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 70<br> <font color=#FF0000>(10/31/01 4:49:01 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub88.ezboard.com/fepicheroes73161frm21.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=24.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Excited About Thurgadin Armour</span><hr size=1> Im there!!!<br>
